{"tid":409441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[涼薄嘅主席] 轟鄺俊宇人身攻擊！馬時亨：成世最憎人話我涼薄","createTime":"2017-09-22T05:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T15:26:24.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bde5d754d6d206c5674088d92b7ff87b39ab9b1f","tid":409441,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:06:19.000Z","msg":"今年二月港鐵尖沙咀站發生縱火案，有議員及傷者近日批評該公司第三者保險未有賠償，港鐵（066）主席馬時亨在倫敦出席貿發局活動時，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>重申港鐵是受害者角色，並不點名批評立法會議員鄺俊宇指控他涼薄、做騷，屬人身攻擊，「成世人最憎有人話我涼薄，係冇智慧嘅言論。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n馬時亨指，港鐵尖沙咀站縱火案中，19名傷者中包括中學生，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「我好唔開心，肉體、心靈嘅受傷，用咩錢都不能彌補」</strong></span>。他又透露事後曾希望探望該名中學生，不過被婉拒。<br />\n<br />\n他重申在該事件上，「唔係我哋做得唔好，明白事理嘅都知我哋都係受害者」，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有人曾提議港鐵發放恩恤金，他解釋港鐵作為上市公司，原則性問題需要搞清楚，否則先例一開，將會引致後果</strong></span>，但個人而言是非常希望幫助他們，故此事後港鐵發起的募捐行動中，他稱他本人及行政總裁捐款額最多，但未有透露數額。<br />\n<br />\n在是次事件上，馬時亨嘆在原則及同理心上陷入兩難，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「所以諗緊方法點幫佢哋，離不開都係用錢，但未有定案，最終可能是甚麼都幫不到」</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n此外，被問到港鐵研究已久的補貼長期票價機制是否以政府身為股東所收取的股息用來補貼時，馬時亨則指應由政府代為回答，不過早前有消息指出政府對此反應正面。"},{"pid":"2a47e444ac71c011aa8b1a5c6d878d2d6d8cb327","tid":409441,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:06:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170922/57240633\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170922%2F57240633&d=8W6UNhn1qrXi%2BJrxuTVLv%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ebeed225\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170922%2F57240633&h=ee754fd8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170922/57240633</a>"},{"pid":"27499316ee57b7aba369430d0e1811c8eede21a9","tid":409441,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:07:42.000Z","msg":"用愛心補償受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1737e8bf8ea523a0c2381c50d6ba20c61b4b7e45","tid":409441,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"最終可能是甚麼都幫不到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c48e4a00f2b73badf270296f4e268870c72ccb5","tid":409441,"uid":52881,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:54:53.000Z","msg":"我大人啤你賤人得，你賤人啤我大人唔得<br />\n<br />\n好大o既官威呀"},{"pid":"279737d2fb0bd35fc89a790694a83d9c4a10e9d3","tid":409441,"uid":73856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"最終可能是甚麼都幫不到"},{"pid":"601cecc851022f9cf8aa84eeebd8ef7cee350341","tid":409441,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最終可能是甚麼都幫不到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaee486b9432afeff3ee9ad85ad650e15831ed87","tid":409441,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:01:02.000Z","msg":"咁你真係好涼薄丫嘛<br />\n錢係彌償唔晒，但你條屎忽鬼連錢都唔肯畀。"},{"pid":"0795837bf46b800e8965cbe21d07ae8a90931524","tid":409441,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:16:10.000Z","msg":"咁你咪捐一個月人工出嚟囉.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb30b4f0e6991001a9cc176b1c2a7da1e407b9b","tid":409441,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"事實佢又冇講錯 又唔係狗鐵搞單野出黎 班垃圾受害者咁鍾意錢就民事索償返個原兇"},{"pid":"038d078451054b24928b25ba6f19b728cdeaee12","tid":409441,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:18:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">涼薄</span></span>"},{"pid":"1f56c55e13fb2124b777f27a6dac976db252364d","tid":409441,"uid":31798,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:31:58.000